## BP configuration for Node A (engine ID 1 = ipn:1.x)

1

a scheme ipn 'ipnfw' 'ipnadminep'

a endpoint ipn:1.0 x
a endpoint ipn:1.1 x
a endpoint ipn:1.2 x

## LTP protocol — class 1 = best effort, 100 = max nominal rate Mbps
a protocol ltp 1400 100

## Induct: receive from LTP engine 1 (local)
a induct ltp 1 ltpcli

## Outduct: send via LTP engine 2 (remote)
a outduct ltp 2 ltpclo

s
